2c07f201-db3f-4ddf-a994-cce06109cb90.title: Squire
2c07f201-db3f-4ddf-a994-cce06109cb90.text: Hello. I am the squire to Sir Vyvin.

options.text: And how is life as a squire?
Wouldn't you prefer to be a squire for me?

346068fe-b7e8-4dae-8c86-c4748abac5d0.title: <player>
346068fe-b7e8-4dae-8c86-c4748abac5d0.text: And how is life as a squire?

a9698e7b-f91c-413a-8b0e-efb75624f878.title: Squire
a9698e7b-f91c-413a-8b0e-efb75624f878.text:
Well, Sir Vyvin is a good guy to work for, however,
I'm in a spot of trouble today. I've gone and lost Sir
Vyvin's sword!

options.text: Do you know where you lost it?
I can make a new sword if you like...

93732dce-f064-4d02-8733-7267b32e841c.title: <player>
93732dce-f064-4d02-8733-7267b32e841c.text: Wouldn't you prefer to be a squire for me?

92ec20c0-b87e-4af5-ba67-0f4c7bcdddd1.title: Squire
92ec20c0-b87e-4af5-ba67-0f4c7bcdddd1.text: No, sorry, I'm loyal to Sir Vyvin.

b8ebbb9c-6a34-483b-9f53-f8f3b09484ac.title: Squire
b8ebbb9c-6a34-483b-9f53-f8f3b09484ac.text:
He doesn't know yet. I was hoping I could think of
something to do before he does find out, But I find
myself at a loss.

options.text: Well, do you know the VAGUE AREA you lost it?
I can make a new sword if you like...
Well, the kingdom is fairly abundant with swords...
Well, I hope you find it soon.

904f75de-10c0-427f-b737-40b63e4f7613.title: <player>
904f75de-10c0-427f-b737-40b63e4f7613.text: Well, I hope you find it soon.

3d07a730-1e8d-4f23-b842-37bed963976e.title: Squire
3d07a730-1e8d-4f23-b842-37bed963976e.text:
Yes, me too. I'm not looking forward to telling Vyvin
I've lost it. He's going to want it for the parade next
week as well.

79e0a491-c405-48e7-a217-61ec40e3702a.title: <player>
79e0a491-c405-48e7-a217-61ec40e3702a.text: Do you know where you lost it?

acecf5a2-aff8-42b3-ade8-b88927eb969d.title: Squire
acecf5a2-aff8-42b3-ade8-b88927eb969d.text:
Well now, if I knew THAT it wouldn't be lost, now
would it?

79e380c8-e615-4b7e-9a4d-899669c4320e.title: <player>
79e380c8-e615-4b7e-9a4d-899669c4320e.text: Well, the kingdom is fairly abundant with swords...

7dd3c268-a187-482c-bd91-b5d5f3916ae7.title: Squire
7dd3c268-a187-482c-bd91-b5d5f3916ae7.text:
Yes. You can get bronze swords anywhere. But THIS
isn't any old sword.

b676a2de-9fd0-4504-aa76-6b363739e2a1.title: Squire
b676a2de-9fd0-4504-aa76-6b363739e2a1.text:
The thing is, this sword is a family heirloom. It has been
passed down through Vyvin's family for five
generations! It was originally made by the Imcando
dwarves, who were

9d63cc7a-9947-4137-a38b-f31e67a7825a.title: Squire
9d63cc7a-9947-4137-a38b-f31e67a7825a.text:
a particularly skilled tribe of dwarven smiths. I doubt
anyone could make it in the style they do.

options.text: So would these dwarves make another one?
Well I hope you find it soon.

00d8461a-fca9-4f8a-92b6-1876e1b94e42.title: <player>
00d8461a-fca9-4f8a-92b6-1876e1b94e42.text: Well, do you know the VAGUE AREA you lost it in?

010210ae-d5b0-4a85-931a-9c92ebe59b0d.title: Squire
010210ae-d5b0-4a85-931a-9c92ebe59b0d.text:
No. I was carrying it for him all the way from where
he had it stored in Lumbridge. It must have slipped
from my pack during the trip, and you know what
people are like these days...

580dcbba-204d-4c57-a083-c9b1ccb3a085.title: Squire
580dcbba-204d-4c57-a083-c9b1ccb3a085.text:
Someone will have just picked it up and kept it for
themselves.

options.text: I can make a new sword if you like...
Well, the kingdom is fairly abundant with swords...
Well, I hope you find it soon.

9e81b39d-5b32-4ae2-99a6-5751c81c849d.title: <player>
9e81b39d-5b32-4ae2-99a6-5751c81c849d.text: I can make a new sword if you like...

33ea765f-b346-4937-be20-8e08f6f86b38.title: Squire
33ea765f-b346-4937-be20-8e08f6f86b38.text:
Thanks for the offer. I'd be surprised if you could
though.

209e5a88-25b4-4b6e-8f50-6031060eed9a.title: <player>
209e5a88-25b4-4b6e-8f50-6031060eed9a.text: So would these dwarves make another one?

3178946d-2dec-4ee9-98b2-731899b09cb2.title: Squire
3178946d-2dec-4ee9-98b2-731899b09cb2.text:
I'm not a hundred percent sure the Imcando tribe
exists anymore. I should think Reldo, the palace
librarian in Varrock, will know; he has done a lot of
research on the races of Gielinor.

50401d9e-00da-46cb-a6e7-bd9123ab8799.title: Squire
50401d9e-00da-46cb-a6e7-bd9123ab8799.text:
I don't suppose you could try and track down the
Imcando dwarves for me? I've got so much work to
do...

options.text: Ok, I'll give it a go.
No, I've got lots of mining work to do.

e6d4e008-7b93-48b8-ba51-9c4011927b2a.title: <player>
e6d4e008-7b93-48b8-ba51-9c4011927b2a.text: No. I've got lots of mining work to do.

bc08c66e-1ee5-4a66-bf1a-602fb2848d8e.title: Squire
bc08c66e-1ee5-4a66-bf1a-602fb2848d8e.text: Oh man... I'm in such trouble...

ffd09a0f-bfe1-4f58-8bed-f503162c1d11.title: <player>
ffd09a0f-bfe1-4f58-8bed-f503162c1d11.text: Ok, I'll give it a go.

b874dbc3-c184-4191-83f7-efa6b361fbab.title: Squire
b874dbc3-c184-4191-83f7-efa6b361fbab.text:
Thank you very much! As I say, the best place to start
should be with Reldo...

0c64c2e9-c91c-4708-b296-8fe76a559bb6.title: Squire
0c64c2e9-c91c-4708-b296-8fe76a559bb6.text: So how are you doing getting a sword?

4e210bba-83f8-4026-b754-35f000d2be63.title: <player>
4e210bba-83f8-4026-b754-35f000d2be63.text: I'm looking for Imcando dwarves to help me.

7fa8ffa4-6c21-4b6b-82c7-91ad98aafbe3.title: Squire
7fa8ffa4-6c21-4b6b-82c7-91ad98aafbe3.text:
Please try and find them quickly... I am scared Sir
Vyvin will find out!

76e044fa-1217-41d0-93e1-b6edc77c2be1.title: Squire
76e044fa-1217-41d0-93e1-b6edc77c2be1.text: So how are you doing getting a sword?

c6df4df2-60c9-4485-b450-41712f00fb1e.title: <player>
c6df4df2-60c9-4485-b450-41712f00fb1e.text:
I've found an Imcando dwarf but he needs a picture of
the sword before he can make it.

6e5181bf-d6fe-4858-8dd9-5677f9f9cd89.title: Squire
6e5181bf-d6fe-4858-8dd9-5677f9f9cd89.text:
A picture eh? Hmmm.... The only one I can think of is
in a small portrait of Sir Vyvin's father... Sir Vyvin
keeps it in a cupboard in his room I think.

126afc8c-20d4-443a-905f-5d7451c99599.title: <player>
126afc8c-20d4-443a-905f-5d7451c99599.text: Ok, I'll try and get that then.

9157d465-b134-4942-89d7-3ef644a598ed.title: Squire
9157d465-b134-4942-89d7-3ef644a598ed.text:
Please don't let him catch you! He MUSTN'T know
what happened!

fc8703d7-7d6a-4f02-90a2-d90458484560.title: Squire
fc8703d7-7d6a-4f02-90a2-d90458484560.text: So how are you doing getting a sword?

7368b9a2-41b4-4f55-9667-16d217fc5688.title: <player>
7368b9a2-41b4-4f55-9667-16d217fc5688.text:
I have the picture.
I'll just take it to the dwarf now!

4ab90945-3e6a-490c-9032-ec0b16eae727.title: <player>
4ab90945-3e6a-490c-9032-ec0b16eae727.text: I didn't get the picture yet.

34e6d6ac-2df6-4f40-9cad-da46d3584b3f.title: Squire
34e6d6ac-2df6-4f40-9cad-da46d3584b3f.text:
Please try and get it quickly... I am scared Sir Vyvin
will find out!

e8be471a-a767-4e18-b0a7-3f279a74a32e.title: Squire
e8be471a-a767-4e18-b0a7-3f279a74a32e.text: So how are you doing getting a sword?

81e0d1e7-3398-4ba8-9c74-6b0657a6f14f.title: <player>
81e0d1e7-3398-4ba8-9c74-6b0657a6f14f.text:
I've found a dwarf who will make the sword.
I've just got to find the materials for it now!

17942470-d23d-4ffa-8ea3-8d73d290efbf.title: Note
17942470-d23d-4ffa-8ea3-8d73d290efbf.text: Need dialogue if has dropped sword

9ba3bda0-8cdd-4715-9dd4-c01130bc8ec9.title: <player>
9ba3bda0-8cdd-4715-9dd4-c01130bc8ec9.text: I have retrieved your sword for you.

53622b73-d238-474c-b263-cd63398c1449.title: Squire
53622b73-d238-474c-b263-cd63398c1449.text:
Thank you, thank you, thank you! I was seriously
worried I would have to own up to Sir Vyvin!

ddf36f81-4521-41f7-afd6-9ab7f9b8dcd8.title: Squire
ddf36f81-4521-41f7-afd6-9ab7f9b8dcd8.text:
Hello friend! Many thanks for all of your help! Vyvin
never even realised it was a different sword, and I still
have my job!

6d4660a9-43ef-4165-b30a-d9904c6fb629.title: <player>
6d4660a9-43ef-4165-b30a-d9904c6fb629.text: I'm glad the new sword worked out alright.
